sequenceDiagram
    actor Customer as 客户
    participant UI as 转账入口/后续页面
    participant API as atm.js/http.js
    participant C as TransactionController
    participant S as TransactionServiceImpl
    participant E as GlobalExceptionHandler
    Customer->>UI: 选择转账并输入目标账户/金额
    UI->>API: transfer(sessionId, targetAccountNo, amount)
    API->>C: POST /api/atm/transactions/transfer
    C->>S: transfer(TransferRequest)
    S-->>E: ApiException(501)
    E-->>API: Result(code=501)
    API-->>UI: 交易模块骨架提示
    UI-->>Customer: 展示第二次迭代待实现

